title: Pretty Little Liars star Keegan Allen poses in his pants
text:
Pip Ellwood-Hughes Gay Focus News , Pretty Little Liars 
Pretty Little Liars star Keegan Allen leaves very little to the imagination in a photo posted by James Franco. 
Keegan is starring in King Cobra, Franco’s new film based on the real life murder of gay adult film producer Bryan Kocis. Disney star Garrett Clayton will be appearing in the film as pornstar Brent Corrigan and it seems Franco himself will be in the movie too! 
In the snap posted to Instagram by Franco, Keegan is wearing nothing but a pair of budgie smugglers and a medallion around his neck. Franco appears in the image shirtless with his underwear peeping out of his trousers. Oh and did we mention that Keegan is pretty greased up too? 
Someone really should tell Spencer what her boyfriend gets up to when he’s not in Rosewood… 
Check out the smoking hot picture below: A photo posted by James Franco (@jamesfrancotv) on Oct 20, 2015 at 8:39am PDT
